'''Clause IV'''（[[英文]]：第四條款）係[[英國]][[工黨]]嗰黨章嗰第四條款，話嗰係箇隻黨嗰目標理念同到價值觀。等[[1995年]]佢拕修改前，佢一徑備受爭議。

Clause IV係[[1917年]][[11月]]拕Sidney Webb草寫正嗰，第年拕寫進黨章。佢嗰內容係：

{{divbox|red||To secure for the workers by hand or by brain the full fruits of their industry and the most equitable distribution thereof that may be possible upon the basis of the common ownership of the means of production, distribution and exchange, and the best obtainable system of popular administration and control of each industry or service.}}

